      "layout": "The page primarily employs a max-width contained layout even though `pageMaxWidth` is null, evident by content being centered with significant whitespace on either side. The hero section features oversized, decorative serif typography with a smaller, pill-shaped button overlayed. Content follows a rhythmic pattern of large media blocks (videos/images) paired with adjacent text descriptions, often in a two-column arrangement. Vertical spacing is generous, creating distinct sections without visible dividers. The navigation appears to be a minimal footer with contact information, client lists, and features.",
