      "description": "BUTT STUDIO employs a high-contrast aesthetic blending stark whitespace with deeply saturated accents. Typography is a focal point, using a mix of classic serif and system sans-serif for clear hierarchy. Layouts are spacious, allowing content and bold elements to breathe, while interactions are subtly animated. The overall impression is one of artful simplicity, where carefully chosen details make a strong visual statement without clutter.",
